Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.51,0:22:44.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\fs38\pos(640,645)}Perfect Crime Party
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.85,0:22:49.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Party嗎 謝謝
